{"tid":990043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派四千蚊咁大件事 環保撚死晒去邊","createTime":"2019-01-21T09:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T05:22:54.000Z","uid":198834,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"757b192e9f1d13e80074806c00d88fc2e3320fb0","tid":990043,"uid":198834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:55:26.000Z","msg":"一份申請表四版紙<br />\n證明文件副本三份<br />\n又要入信封寄出去<br />\n財爺話有280萬人合資格<br />\n即係派一次錢浪費咗千幾兩千萬張紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲樹要種幾耐先可以種返出嚟<br />\n環保撚死撚晒去邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收嗰四千蚊就即刻聲都唔敢出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正苦又係弱撚智<br />\n嗰三億行政費撥少少出嚟整個system網上交<br />\n好過請人收信拆信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n封信平郵寄出去<br />\n一陣啲人就咁貼張兩蚊郵票唔夠郵費<br />\n又或者寄失咗<br />\n邊個負責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最大問題係封信全部個人資料<br />\n又身份證地址證明提款卡副本<br />\n俾人盗用咗點撚算<br />\n<br />\n仆街環保撚淨係識嘈人用飲管<br />\n啲樹冇鼻就唔使理？<br />\n正苦而家帶頭鼓勵全香港人唔好支持環保喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72470cf1ebfd542e707b1b52abb9c66c57de7122","tid":990043,"uid":199251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:04:29.000Z","msg":"四千蚊就可以買起環保撚嘅虛榮心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70d5c1aa841081415b9cc808e6d8a706e5f9191","tid":990043,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"環保撚一定係用環保紙print 唔好怪錯佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd77f638998e96c0d8fe7c40a8dead2c72254b6","tid":990043,"uid":198834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f70d5c1aa841081415b9cc808e6d8a706e5f9191","tid":990043,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"